NPC: Kurron Ni, rare spawn near the docks, swim or invis to get to him if KoS<br>
Hail him and say: &quot;I agree&quot;<br>
Give him 3 Darkforge ammor pieces (Temple of Sol Ro quest items). Helm Chest and Leggings and 900pp<br>
<br>
Then say &quot;what mission&quot;, he will then attack you. U must slay him. He hits for a max of 160 and is level 55. suggested 2 groups of 50.<br>
<br>
Loot a &quot;Note to Duriek&quot;<br>
<br>
NOTE: You MUST first hand in these items or he will not drop the note. This has been tested and confirmed.<br>
<br>
Next go to Paineel and find Duriek upstrais in the newbie area. hand him the note. He will say &quot;take this for your efforts&quot; yet you will receive nothing. this is normal. do not be alarmed.<br>
<br>
say &quot;what apprentice&quot;<br>
then say &quot;I will take his place&quot; or &quot;I will take your apprentice's place&quot;<br>
<br>
Duriek asks for a cough elixir.<br>
<br>
Go to Neriak and give an Ogre named Smaka 1000pp in Foriegn Quarter for the Elixir.<br>
<br>
Back to Duriek. Give him the Elixir. He will tell you about corrupted ghoulbane's. Go to the hole and collect a Tome dropped from a Ratman Guard, level 55, High MR, High HP, Hits for 370. Raid force needed, these guards can be slowed.<br>
<br>
(Guards are found by taking a left after entering the first fortress and then another left and down past the pool. between this area and the old city is where the guards spawn and patrol)<br>
<br>
Take the Tome and give it to Duriek. He will then say that he needs the following items to complete the ghoulbane.<br>
<br>
I) Blade of Abrogation<br>
II) Soul Leech, Dark Sword of Blood<br>
III) Ghoulbane<br>
IV) Decrepit Sheath from a Qeynos side quest.<br>
<br>
Blade of Abrogation is dropped from Thunder Spirit Princess on Island One in PoS. Level 53, 1 group of 50s can take her.<br>
<br>
Soul Leech is found in PoF from Cazic Thule (70), Fright (55), Dread (55), or Terror (55). Fright and Dread will hit for up to 500 and DT every 45 seconds. Terror is the most difficult, melee around 300-400 and has a cold based AoE of close to 500. if SvC is 180 he will hit for 300 on AoE. Raid Party needed. 4 groups or more.<br>
<br>
Ghoulbane is found in Upper Guk or Quested. If you want to get the item as a drop. you must kill A Froglok Shin Lord, level 30, is a Paladin. This fight can be solo'd.<br>
<br>
Decrepid Sheath is retrieved by giving Teydar 3 items. He is located in Qeynos Sewers.<br>
<br>
1.) Decrepit Hide, found in PoH from Ashenbone Drakes, level 53, about 12 spawn in hate total. 6 on each floor. the Hide is a RARE drop.<br>
2.) Drake Spine, found in RM, on Rharzar, level 55, rare spawn. around 7k hit points. one group of 50+. he spawns on 'drake hill' regular drakes are PH.<br>
3.) Enchanted Platinum Bar, storebought.<br>
<br>
Give the 3 items to Teydar to get the Decrepit Sheath. Then take the Sheath, and 3 swords to Duriek and recieve A Corrupted Ghoulbane (1hs, dmg: 16, dly: 34, effect: dismiss undead, Sk only)<br>
<br>
You will then be sent to seek out Lhranc in CoM. who spawns at approx 0,0. just before the reaver area. in a large hut right past the big goo house. He has no known PH. He will reveal what he needs to forge Inoruuk's Curse when u speak to him.<br>
<br>
1.) Heart of an Innocent<br>
Go talk to Knarthenne Skurle in Tox Forest<br>
You will need good TrueSpirit faction (which has been raising with every turnin to this point)<br>
He will give you a scrollcase (2 slot container).<br>
<br>
You need to go to The Hole and talk to Caradon who spawns in the Jail. (past the Ratmen from before), he needs a key to get out of his cell. the Key is found from Mimics which spawn in the bank area. the key is RARE drop.<br>
<br>
When you give him the Key Caradon and Kyreene (who spawns at key turn in) will attack you. The best idea is to simply Mess Caradorn (his spawn time is 3 days) and fight Kyreene, YOU DO NOT NEED TO KILL CARADON. after killing Kyreene loot &quot;Blood of Kyreena&quot; and &quot;Heart of Kyreena&quot;. place heart in the scrollcase and combine. U will then have &quot;Heart of an Innocent&quot;. 3 groups needed for this encounter.<br>
<br>
2.) The Will of Innoruuk<br>
Go to Kerra Island and speak with Marl Kastana (spawns on ridge). This mob spawns twice. You need the 1st version at this point. If the mob responds to &quot;what prophecy&quot; you have the 2nd version.<br>
<br>
The 1st version will give you a note to take to Gerot Kastana in Paineel. Gerot will then give u an item to return to Marl. (this will spawn the 2nd Marl) DO NOT SKIP THIS PART. U GET FACTION FOR COMPLETING IT.<br>
<br>
say &quot;what prophecy&quot; and &quot;I will complete the ritual&quot;<br>
give him the Blood of Kyreena and he will give you a Dark Shroud<br>
<br>
Take the Shroud to Ghost of Glohnor in the Hole. A Skeleton of Glohnor will spawn when u give the ghost the shroud. Level 56, High MR, Cannot snare. clear teh room that the ghost is in before engaging as wanderers will mana tap u. 2 groups of 50+<br>
<br>
2 items will drop. Mummy wrappings of Glohnor and Head of Glohnor<br>
<br>
Take the wrappings back to Marl (the 2nd version) and he will give you &quot;Will of Innoruuk&quot;<br>
<br>
3.) Head of the Valiant<br>
Got back to Gerot Kastane in Paineel and give him the Head of Glohnor and he will give you &quot;Head of the Valiant&quot;<br>
<br>
Take the Corrupted Ghoulbane, Heart of an Innocent, Will of Innoruuk, and Head of the Valiant to Lhranc in CoM. and you will get your Epic...<br>
<br>
Innoruuk's Curse<br>
LORE ITEM MAGIC ITEM NO DROP <br>
Damage: 40<br>
Delay: 45 <br>
Ratio: 1.125 Amazing <br>
Str: +20 Dex: +15 Int: +15 Magic Resist: +15 Fire Resist: +10 Cold Resist: +10 Poison Resist: +5 Disease Resist: +5 HP: +60 Mana: +40 <br>
Weight: 5.0 <br>
Weapon Skill: Two Hand Slash <br>
Classes: Shadowknight <br>
Races: Iksar Ogre Troll Dark Elf Erudite Human <br>
Inventory Slot: Primary Melee <br>
Effect: Soul Consumption<br>
3: Decrease Hitpoints by 50 per tick<br>
Type: Triggered <br>
Charges: Unlimited <br>
